lead_paragraph: Colin Kaepernick jerseys were the top-selling jersey on the National Football League's official online store on Tuesday, after he protested racial injustice and police brutality in the United States.

headline.print_headline: Kaepernick Jersey Becomes NFL Best Seller After Anthem Protest
